name: MOBO // Drop n Bounce
description:
Do you ever just mope around and you feel kinda tired and you can't be bothered doing anything and there's stuff you should be doing, but you'd rather take a nap and you have creative block and then out of nowhere you hear a great tune and then BOOM... Go time!!!

Submission for the book "Prosthetic Reality V2"
